HEADWORD: Thalassinian
<hw>Thal`as*sin"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of <fam>Thalassinidae</fam>, a family of burrowing
macrurous Crustacea, having a long and soft abdomen.</def>⟦br⟧
